\id JUD YUD Soli Bible 65 
\h Yuda 
\toc1 Kalata ya Yuda 
\toc2 Yuda 
\toc3 Yuda 
\mt2 Kalata ya 
\mt1 Yuda 
\imt1 BUSANSUUSHI 
\ip Kusansulula libuku lya Yuda. Kalata ikute kukwiweti Yuda yalalembewa ne mwine Yuda. Yuda walalisansulula eti ni mukwabo Jemusi kayi ne mukwabo Yesu. Neco cila bonekengeti ni mukwabo Yesu (Yud 1 ) Nomba nkatucinshi cena na kalata iyi yalalembelwa ku mubungano uli onse, nomba pacebo cakwamba sha mumabala amucipangano cisa cakaindi, mpani Yuda walalembela ku bantu ba Ciyuda. Necikabeco, kalata iyi walailembela kuli bantu bonse abo balakwiwa kayi basunika kuli Lesa Bata kayi abo babambililwa Yesu Klistu (Yuda 1). Kalata iyi yalalembewa mucaka ca 60 A.D. Kalata iyi walailembela kuli baklistu bonse kubacenjesha kwambeti, nkabatakonkanga beshi kwiyisha bandemishibili (Yud 4). Yuda kayi lasebenseshenga mabala amucipangano cisa cakaindi nebyo byalikwinshika kwambeti abisansulule cena kubantu. Kalata iyi yakoshanako ne kalata yatubili ya Petulo palwinshibo lwa beyishi bandemishibili Yuda 4, 2 Petulo 2:1 Ne pacebo cabangelo kayi ne sha Sodomu ne Gomola. 
\iot Mitwi ya makani 
\io1 Cakutanguna Yuda lambilinga bbeshi kubala kalata iyi Yuda 1-2 
\io1 Lasansululunga ncalalembelenga kalata iyi pacebo cakubacenjesha pali beshi kwiyisha bandemishibili Yuda 3-4 
\io1 Panyuma pakendi labapanga mikoshanyo mumabala amucipangano cakaindi Yuda 5-16. Kayi labambilinga mobelela kuba kumbwila abo balico Yuda 17-23. Cakupwililisha lalumbunga Lesa Yud 24-25 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Njame Yuda musebenshi wa Yesu Klistu, ndemukwabo Jemusi. Ndalembelenga njamwe omwalakwiwa ne Lesa omwekala mu lusuno lwa Lesa Bata omwashinkililwa ne Yesu Klistu.  
\v 2 Nkumbo ne lumuno kayi ne lusuno lwesula bibe nenjamwe. 
\p  
\v 3 Mobanse bame, ndayandishishanga kumulembela kalata kwambeti ndimwambile shalupulusho lwetu twense. Nomba lino ndabono kwambeti caina kumulembela nekumusenga mwangofu kwambeti mulwane nkondo yakucingilisha lushomo Lesa ndwalapa bantu kankanda kamowa.  
\v 4 Ndamulembelenga pakwinga bantu nabambi batanyumfwili Lesa bakute kwiyisha biyisho byabwepeshi balengili pakati penu mwakutabenshiba. Aba ebantu mbwalamba Lesa mu Mabala Aswepa mumisemano yakunyuma kwambeti nakabape cisubulo. Pakwinga bakute kupindamuna makani alambanga lusuno lwa Lesa kwambeti, babepeshelemo bensanga bufule. Ebakute kukana Yesu Klistu Mwami wetu.  
\v 5 Lino ndayandanga kumwanushako nabimbi nambi mubishi kendi, kwambeti Lesa walapulusha mushobo wa Islayeli kufuma ku Injipito, mpwalashina bonse babula kumushoma.  
\v 6 Kayi kamwanukani bangelo balabula kwikuta ne bwendeleshi bwabo bwelela, balashiya musena Lesa ngwalabapa. Neco Lesa wabasunga ncetani shitapu mu mushinshe mpaka busuba bwalombolosho.  
\v 7 Kayi kamwanukani minshi ibili ya Sodomu ne Gomola yalikuba yabambana. Umo bantu mobali kwinsa bufule ne bintu nabimbi byasafwana bitayandiki ku muntu. Lesa walabapa cisubulo kwambeti cibe cilesho kuli bonse. 
\p  
\v 8 Nabo bantu aba balenshinga cimocimo, balakonkelenga maloto alepishinga mibili yabo, balakananga bwendeleshi bwa Lesa, balatukananga bilengwa byakwilu byalemekwa.  
\v 9 Nomba Mikayeli mukulene wa bangelo mpobalikulondola ne Satana pakulwanina mubili wa Mose, uliya kumunyanshapo, walamboweti, “Lesa akukanse!”  
\v 10 Nomba bantu aba bakute lisongwe ne pabintu mbyebateshi, balo ncobeshi ni mano acisemwa mbuli abanyama, ebintu bilabashininga.  
\v 11 Bakute malele pakwinga balakonkelenga nshila njalamanta Kaini. Kayi mbuli ncalensa Balamu, balawili mubwipishi cebo cakuyandishisha mali. Balamupandukili Lesa mbuli calensa Kola, neco naboyo balonongeke  
\v 12 Aba ebalepishinga mibungano yenu yalusuno. Baliya nsoni balalinga pamo ne njamwe, balayandangowa byabo. Balyeti makumbi ilanyakangwa ne mpepo, makumbi abula mfula. Balyeti bitondo bitaseme bisepo pacindi cakendi, bitondo ibyo bantu mbyebalashukulu miyanda bilafwililili.  
\v 13 Balyeti mankape apa lwenje, bakute kupulisha mapofu abintu byabo byasafwana. Balyeti nyenyenshi shilataiki nshila. Neco Lesa wabasungila mu mushinshe wanjobe bani utapu.  
\v 14 Enoki wamusemano wacisanu ne cibili kufumina kuli Adamu walalalukapo sha bantu aba mpwalambeti, “Bonani Lesa pamo ne bangelo batabelengeke lesanga  
\v 15 kombolosha bantu bonse. Kubapa cisubulo pancito shabo shaipa nshebalensa, kayi ne maswi abo aipa ngobalikumwamba.”  
\v 16 Aba endibo beshikutungula, batalumbu bilenshinga banabo, beshikukonkelowa lunkumbwa lwaipa, beshikulitunta, beshikuyandowa kulyela masuku pamitwi ya banabo. 
\s1 Kucenjesha ne malailile 
\p  
\v 17 Nomba amwe anukani ncemwalambilwa nebatumwa ba Mwami wetu Yesu Klistu.  
\v 18 Balamwambileti, “Mumasuba akumapwililisho, nikukabe bantu baminyansho, bantu beshikukonkela lunkumbwa lwabo.”  
\v 19 Aba bantu ebakute kuleta kupansana, bakutekuyandowa byamucishi, mu myoyo yabo muliya Mushimu Uswepa sobwe.  
\v 20 Nomba amwe nyumfwanani kwambeti buyumi bwenga pantangu kabuli bwashimpa pa lushomo lwaswepa. Kamupailanga mungofu ya Mushimu Uswepa.  
\v 21 Ikalani mu lusuno lwa Lesa mpomulapembelelenga Mwami wetu Yesu Klistu uyo eshakamupe buyumi butapu munkumbo shakendi. 
\p  
\v 22 Balesheni nkumbo abo bacitonshanya.  
\v 23 Nomba nabambi mubapulushe pakubasompola mumulilo. Nabambi mubaleshe nkumbo mwabuyowa, nsombi mupelane ne byakufwala byabo byatundubila ne lunkumbwa lwa bwipishi. 
\p  
\v 24 Bulemu bube kuli uyo wela kubula kumuleketi muwile mu bwipishi, uyo wela kumushikisha pamenso abulemu bwakendi kamuli mwabula kampenda kalikonse.  
\v 25 Kuli Lesa mupulushi wetu kupitila muli Yesu Klistu Mwami wetu kube bulemu ne bukulene ne ngofu kayi ne bwendeleshi, kufumina cindi cakunyuma, pacino cindi kayi ne kucindi citapu! Ameni.